"  Dressing:","2  cloves garlic, finely minced","1 teaspoon dried oregano","1 teaspoon Dijon mustard","1/4 cup red wine vinegar","1/2 teaspoon salt","1/2 teaspoon pepper","1/2 cup olive oil","  Salad:","  Salt","1 pound gemelli or other short pasta","3/4  medium English cucumber, peeled, halved lengthwise, cut into 1/4-inch pieces","1  dry pint cherry or grape tomatoes, halved","1/2  large red onion, thinly sliced","1 cup pitted kalamata olives, halved","6 ounces feta, crumbled","3 cups firmly packed baby spinach"